{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Note: This product is in development and subject to change.</strong>\u00a0All content featured is from an in-development Alpha build of the game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Level Editor / Community Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/extras/BuildPlayPublish-01.jpg?t=1735058156\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build new <strong>2.5D platforming experiences\u00a0</strong>with an extensive in-game level editor! Browse the community's creations via integration with Steam Workshop, or publish your own content for others to enjoy. In Restitched, <strong>user-generated content is the heart and soul</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Wardrobe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/extras/StyleYourStuffy-01.jpg?t=1735058156\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stuffy may be cute, but did you know they're also quite stylish? Dress your plush companion from head to toe by mixing and matching cosmetic items spanning multiple categories! You can even take advantage of the 'Design Tool' to recolor items and change their appearance.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Stuffy's Adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/extras/LevelTheming-01.jpg?t=1735058156\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join Stuffy on their defining adventure! In addition to the diverse community content, <strong>Restitched will offer a range of official worlds for you to explore</strong>. In these levels, you'll join Stuffy as they traverse worldwide themes in search of their roots. <strong>Meet new friends, face new foes, collect new assets, and 'restitch' communities unraveled at the hands of tyranny</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These <strong>levels are created entirely in-game using the level editor</strong>, and serve as a prime example of what's possible in Restitched!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Stuffy's Abilities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/extras/ClimbCrawlPush-01.jpg?t=1735058156\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Always prepared for a challenge, Stuffy can take down foes and interact with the environment in several exciting ways! <strong>Push</strong> things around, <strong>climb</strong> along ledges, <strong>crawl</strong> through narrow openings... or use the <strong>Needle 'n Thread</strong> to <strong>slash</strong> down enemies and obstacles, <strong>swing</strong> across gaps, and\u00a0<strong>pull</strong> things toward you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/extras/NeedleAndThreadAbilities-01.jpg?t=1735058156\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Passionately Produced</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As aspiring developers, hobbyist creatives, and gaming enthusiasts, <strong>Trixel Creative developers are building Restitched as a labor of love</strong>. Our team is fueled by passion and consists of industry professionals, students, hobbyists, newcomers, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Restitched is a love letter</strong> to the user-generated content (UGC) and platforming genres, and our many wonderful, nostalgic, inspiring experiences within them!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735058156","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/page.bg.jpg?t=1735058156","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361090/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735058156","capsule_